Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:20.32,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}一直相信著自己內心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:23.03,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}即使 身處的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:28.02,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:34.84,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}只要有著想要保護之物…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:41.72,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}你為誰而伸出了右手？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:47.53,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}釋放出了 數以千計的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:50.10,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}這動作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.04,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}這眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:58.00,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}都讓我心頭一緊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:04.38,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}對你不離不棄




Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园都市第三位的超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光闪闪妹 御坂美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是我失忆前的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上她那突然出现在眼前 一个模子出来的的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这两位耍得团团转的我 上条当麻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 我还没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个“妹妹”的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:56.12,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,400)\pos(100,44)\fs15\fscy94}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:56.12,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,400)\pos(60,60)}{\fscx92}#11{\fscx98\b0} 妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这逃跑的姿态算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股还扭得这么欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在诱惑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提问时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.44,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(470,440)}<Accelerator>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷 一方通行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反射...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在可惜 这跟老子的本质不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.97,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,440)}<Vector>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是“矢量变换”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动量 热量 电量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的矢量 光是碰到我的皮肤就可能进行变更
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然默认是设定为“反射”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下来是双淘汰赛的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正触摸着血液的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让它逆流的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的身体会变成怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对的人就奖励...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安乐的永眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 那家伙跑去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御...坂...？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅一下啊 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话 希望你能陪我们一起到案发现场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 尸体原本...应该在这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年 这里什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的...真的有人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本预定是等作业完成以后就回到你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂先行道歉道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以将你认作御坂妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到头来这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 直到刚才那一刻 我还以为你死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 看你好像完好无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂的确已经死亡了哦 御坂报告道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你 到底抱着什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:50.76,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(453,440)}<Pass>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一 我要跟你对暗号 御坂言出必行道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZXC741ASD852QWE963 御坂试验你道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:06.93,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(223,440)}<Decode>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你不能解读刚才的暗号 你好像不是实验的相关人员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂确认道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这睡袋里面装的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:16.56,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,440)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妹妹哦 御坂回答道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为弃这黑猫而去的事情而道歉 御坂说道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 将动物卷入无用的战斗当中 会让我很不舒服 御坂辩解道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来因为本实验 让你多担心了呢 御坂道歉道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实你用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也知道是你去报警的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在场的御坂 都是御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天 一直跟你接触的御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.14,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,440)}<Series Number>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是标本编号10032
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是这个御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“御坂”应用操纵电力的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让相互间的脑电波相连
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是让其他的御坂共享10032号的记忆罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂补充说明道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:41.72,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,440)}<Level 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:41.72,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(610,440)}<Original>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园都市中仅存的七位超能力者 御坂美琴姐姐大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:48.85,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(604,440)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为量产军用模型而造的体细胞克隆体—妹妹 御坂回答道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是实验罢了 御坂回答道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于详细情况乃机密事项 不能向你说明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这并不带有刑事案件性质 御坂辩明道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对将你卷入到本实验当中 我深感抱歉 御坂低头道歉道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞 小猫就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验？军用？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底为什么要在这里乱逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 那家伙知道这回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于小姬神是吃闲饭的 首先要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 为了老师我 赶快烤肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我先说个在学园都市发生的恐怖故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我可不会被七个不可思议之流就吓哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉焦的部分所含的成分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是致癌物质
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种现实存在的恐怖话题 可不是夏季的风景诗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是计划削减我的食欲 然后自己独占这些肉吗 小姬神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然估计是传阅板报之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬神 请你恳切地应对一下人家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我 就趁这空隙 自顾自烤肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后自顾自吃了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我肚子饿...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少...至少让这孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只让史芬克斯吃点也好...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪当麻这么久都不回来 我还以为要饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 不就是多了一两个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个“豪华绚烂烤肉套装” 是不会让人因量不足而留下遗憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～有肉吃 有肉吃 有肉吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站 第七学区 常盘台初中学生宿舍前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,208号室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到那家伙 我要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问她那个能随随便便就去杀一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人讨厌的实验的内容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呃 是御坂吗 我是上条...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...上条先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我弄错了房间的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟姐姐大人是同房
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这声音好像在哪里听过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 您的声音我好像听过...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是昨天跟姐姐大人幽会的那位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找姐姐大人有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 没啥大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大事还特地跑过来 太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她不在的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找姐姐大人有事的话 我推荐你进里面等着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,208号室 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进 门没上锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会在那以后跟姐姐大人行差踏错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有 肯定没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 看你也不像过来说这种轻佻的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等姐姐大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请坐在那张床上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 这样实在有点不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有得到她本人的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是我的床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...这边就是御坂的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在别人床上干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是变态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“变态”这词我可不能当作没听到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就是这样 虽然不敢跟别人说 但心里却想“这种程度是OK的”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想 就像对着喜欢的女孩子的竖笛接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷掉她自行车的坐鞍之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才这样做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 大小姐学校的真实状况 都是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来你跟御坂同屋 你们同一个年级吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你叫她做“姐姐大人” 还以为你肯定是她学妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里 我的确就是姐姐大人的晚辈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年级也比她低
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是让她的前任室友退出 然后自己补上罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 是在合法范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的敌人也是很多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说这是有力量的人的孽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不觉得连睡同一房间的人都是叛徒 这样会太痛苦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我能认为你就是平常就跟姐姐大人频繁起争执的男士么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄错了的话 也没啥关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我只是想稍微看看作为姐姐大人心灵支柱的男士的样子罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵支柱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这脚步声...糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍监好像来巡房了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 被她知道常盘台女生宿舍有男人在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.74,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,440)}<Teleport>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就用空间移动 送你到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的力量对你不管用？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:19.83,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(550,440)}<Imagine Breaker>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 那个 肯定是因为我的右手...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 请你先躲到床底下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这缝隙 太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井 到晚餐时间了 快到食堂集合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？御坂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人还在补习 估计是拖堂了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有收到这个报告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她过了门限还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室友将负上连带责任 扣一分 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉链？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.07,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,440)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“妹妹”是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.29,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘由量产异能者“妹妹”的运用使“一方通行”向绝对能力的进化法’
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.29,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(204,30)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.29,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(398,30)}<Accelerator Level 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.29,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(540,30)}<Level 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.02,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,440)}<Level 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.06,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,440)}<Tree Diagram>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用树形图设计者预测演算过后的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判断得出 能到达绝对能力者 Level 6的人只有一名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过准备好特定的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照剧本来进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由实战促进其成长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然看不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有吹风 螺旋桨竟然在转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风力发电 是通过螺旋桨转动而发电
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来 通过给予电力 螺旋桨就会转动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的身体 应该总是会发出电磁波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来 跟着这个来追的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写在报告上面的 极具冲击性的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:29.65,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(439,440)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这个背负着妹妹残酷的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就被压垮的御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.73,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(474,440)}<Level 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 绝对能力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学与魔术交错之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事就开始了


